{"id":8120,"date":"2021-10-27T09:51:00","date_gmt":"2021-10-27T02:51:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/?p=8120"},"modified":"2023-11-22T12:50:18","modified_gmt":"2023-11-22T05:50:18","slug":"thong-tin-quy-hoach-duong-vanh-dai-1","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/thong-tin-quy-hoach-duong-vanh-dai-1\/","title":{"rendered":"Th\u00f4ng tin quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t 2021"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1<\/strong> TP.HCM l\u00e0 1 tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb c\u1ea5p I. M\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ban \u0111\u1ea7u cho \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd khi x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0110\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 l\u00e0 nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o ra 1 tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i nhanh h\u01a1n v\u00e0 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng xung quanh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn trung t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111i v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c \u201cl\u00f5i\u201d c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_8140\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8140\" class=\"wp-image-8140 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/6-chot-1-15782345153131646969919.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 - TP HCM\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/600;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8140\" class=\"wp-image-8140 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/6-chot-1-15782345153131646969919.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 - TP HCM\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-8140\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 &#8211; TP HCM<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u01a1i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean x\u1ea3y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng k\u1eb9t xe v\u00e0 \u00f9n t\u1eafc. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb h\u00f3a qu\u00e1 nhanh, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb I. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <strong>Vinhome Land<\/strong> t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u00e0y nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/vinhomes-grand-park\/\"><strong>Vinhomes Grand Park Qu\u1eadn 9<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ebf n\u00e0o l\u00e0 \u0110\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai?<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb l\u1edbn \u0111\u00ea\u0300u x\u00e2y d\u01b0\u0323ng l\u00ean 1 tuy\u00ea\u0301n \u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0300ng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai bao quanh. Vi\u1ec7c d\u00e2n s\u1ed1 \u0111ang ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t t\u0103ng cao \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9o theo h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u0169ng m\u1ecdc l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai n\u00e0y s\u1ebd giu\u0301p hoa\u0300n thi\u00ea\u0323n c\u01a1 s\u1edf ha\u0323 t\u00e2\u0300ng v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n thu\u00e2\u0323n l\u01a1\u0323i cho vi\u1ec7c di chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u01b0 d\u00e2n trong khu v\u01b0\u0323c. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng thu\u0301c \u0111\u00e2\u0309y hoa\u0323t \u0111\u00f4\u0323ng bu\u00f4n b\u00e1n v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8141 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/006791.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u00f4ng tin quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t 2021\" width=\"800\" height=\"535\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/535;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8141\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/006791.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u00f4ng tin quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t 2021\" width=\"800\" height=\"535\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0110ai ( hay c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bao quanh ), kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0323c du\u0300ng \u0111\u00ea\u0309 chi\u0309 nh\u01b0\u0303ng tuy\u00ea\u0301n \u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0300ng l\u01a1\u0301n v\u00e0 cha\u0323y xung quanh tha\u0300nh ph\u00f4\u0301. Nh\u1eefng tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd bao quanh di\u00ea\u0323n ti\u0301ch c\u1ee7a n\u00f4\u0323i \u0111\u00f4, gi\u00fap cho vi\u1ec7c v\u1eadn chuy\u00ea\u0309n trong khu v\u01b0\u0323c tr\u1edf n\u00ean thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 d\u00ea\u0303 da\u0300ng h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111i ti\u0300nh tra\u0323ng g\u00e2y ngh\u1ebdn t\u0103\u0301c giao th\u00f4ng ta\u0323i ca\u0301c khu \u0111\u00f4 thi\u0323 l\u1edbn. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng tuy\u00ea\u0301n \u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0300ng na\u0300y th\u01b0\u01a1\u0300ng s\u1ebd la\u0300 xa l\u1ed9 tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00e1nh ho\u1eb7c nh\u1eefng tuy\u00ea\u0301n cao t\u00f4\u0301c v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00ea\u0301t n\u00f4\u0301i v\u01a1\u0301i c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn qu\u00f4\u0301c l\u00f4\u0323 th\u00f4ng qua ca\u0301c nu\u0301t giao th\u00f4ng tro\u0323ng \u0111i\u00ea\u0309m trong khu \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, UBND th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o \u0111\u0103\u0323c \u0111i\u00ea\u0309m t\u1eebng \u0111\u00f4 thi\u0323 v\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u01b0\u0323ng c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0300ng phu\u0300 h\u01a1\u0323p h\u01a1n v\u01a1\u0301i \u0111i\u0323a th\u00ea\u0301 va\u0300 th\u00f4ng tin quy hoa\u0323ch. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i,\u00a0 TPHCM \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 4 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai bao g\u1ed3m: \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 2, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 4.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_8144\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8144\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8144 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/duong-vanh-dai-1-tphcm1.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0110ai 1\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8144\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8144\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/duong-vanh-dai-1-tphcm1.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0110ai 1\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-8144\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0110ai 1<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 \u0111\u1ebfn khu v\u1ef1c<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u2013\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Gia\u0309m b\u01a1\u0301t a\u0301p l\u01b0\u0323c v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n n\u1ea1n a\u0301ch t\u0103\u0301c giao th\u00f4ng, gi\u00fap nh\u1eefng tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u2013\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa ca\u0301c \u0111i\u0323a ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf l\u00e2n c\u1eadn v\u01a1\u0301i nhau, thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n cho vi\u1ec7c di chuy\u1ec3n nhanh cho\u0301ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00e2\u0300n th\u00f4ng qua 1 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c tuy\u00ea\u0301n \u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0300ng n\u00f4\u0323i \u0111\u00f4. T\u01b0\u0300 \u0111o\u0301 thu\u0301c \u0111\u00e2\u0309y m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd ca\u0301c hoa\u0323t \u0111\u00f4\u0323ng bu\u00f4n b\u00e1n, th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 v\u1eadn t\u1ea3i \u1edf trong khu v\u01b0\u0323c.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u2013\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Hoa\u0300n thi\u00ea\u0323n th\u00eam v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ha\u0323 t\u00e2\u0300ng giao th\u00f4ng c\u01a1 s\u1edf, qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng ta\u0323o n\u00ean s\u01b0\u0323 k\u00ea\u0301t n\u00f4\u0301i \u0111\u00f4\u0300ng b\u00f4\u0323 h\u01a1n gi\u1eefa ca\u0301c tuy\u00ea\u0301n \u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0300ng t\u1ea1i \u0111i\u0323a ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8145 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/pham-van-dong-mot-phan-cua-vanh-dai-1-tphcm.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u00f4ng tin quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t 2021\" width=\"800\" height=\"422\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/422;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8145\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/pham-van-dong-mot-phan-cua-vanh-dai-1-tphcm.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u00f4ng tin quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t 2021\" width=\"800\" height=\"422\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u2013\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 H\u1ec7 th\u00f4\u0301ng giao th\u00f4ng \u1edf t\u1ea1i \u0111i\u0323a ph\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng. V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng d\u00e2n s\u1ed1 \u0111ang ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t t\u0103ng nhanh th\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 1 \u0111i\u00ea\u0300u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng c\u00e2\u0300n thi\u00ea\u0301t gi\u00fap cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n di chuy\u00ea\u0309n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ranh gi\u1edbi ph\u00e2n chia khu v\u1ef1c n\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh \u2013 ngo\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">UBND TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ranh gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n chia gi\u1eefa n\u1ed9i \u2013 ngo\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh x\u1eed ph\u1ea1t c\u00e1c vi ph\u1ea1m trong giao th\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ed9.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh s\u1ebd g\u1ed3m \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1eb1m b\u00ean trong \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1, cung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e9p k\u00edn: Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 1A (t\u1eeb n\u00fat giao Th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c) \u2013 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Linh \u2013 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ea5n l\u00ean c\u1ea7u Ph\u00fa M\u1ef9 &#8211; C.Ph\u00fa M\u1ef9 &#8211; v.\u0111ai \u0110\u00f4ng \u2013 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ecb \u0110\u1ecbnh \u2013 Xa l\u1ed9 \u2013 n\u00fat giao Th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_8143\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8143\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8143 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/duong-vanh-dai-1-tphcm.png\" alt=\"B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0110ai 1 TPHCM\" width=\"800\" height=\"597\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/597;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8143\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8143\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/duong-vanh-dai-1-tphcm.png\" alt=\"B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0110ai 1 TPHCM\" width=\"800\" height=\"597\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-8143\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0110ai 1 TPHCM<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ri\u00eang \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Linh th\u00ec do c\u00f3 \u0111o\u1ea1n nh\u1ecf \u0111i qua B\u00ecnh Ch\u00e1nh v\u00e0 tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 1A c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111i qua \u0111\u1ecba ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a t\u1ec9nh B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong ph\u1ea1m vi ph\u1ea1t \u201ct\u0103ng n\u1eb7ng\u201d n\u00ean n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 vi ph\u1ea1m ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t \u1edf m\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin <a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/grand-marina-sai-gon-ba-son-quan-1\/\"><strong>Grand Marina Saigon Qu\u1eadn 1<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0110ai 1 TPHCM<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ebfn nay, tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0110ai 1 \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n kh\u00e9p k\u00edn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u1eb1m g\u1ea7n trung t\u00e2m TP.HCM nh\u1ea5t. UBND TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ranh gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n chia gi\u1eefa n\u1ed9i \u2013 ngo\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u1ea1n 1: T\u1eeb ng\u00e3 t\u01b0 Linh \u0110\u00f4ng (n\u00fat giao\u00a0 gi\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Ph\u1ea1m V\u0103n \u0110\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0111ai 2) cho \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng xoay Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n. \u0110o\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y d\u00e0i 8,5 km g\u1ed3m 12 l\u00e0n xe v\u1edbi l\u1ed9 gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 60m. \u0110o\u1ea1n 1 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh thi c\u00f4ng tr\u00f9ng v\u1edbi con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Ph\u1ea1m V\u0103n \u0110\u1ed3ng.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_8142\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8142\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8142 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/duong-vanh-dai-1-tphcm.jpg\" alt=\"Quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0110ai 1\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/600;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8142\" class=\"size-full wp-image-8142\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/duong-vanh-dai-1-tphcm.jpg\" alt=\"Quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0110ai 1\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-8142\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0110ai 1<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u1ea1n 2: D\u00e0i 4,8km t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng xoay Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e1i S\u01a1n cho \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e3 t\u01b0 B\u1ea3y Hi\u1ec1n. \u0110o\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y \u0111i tr\u00f9ng v\u1edbi tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng: B\u1ea1ch \u0110\u1eb1ng \u2013 H\u1ed3ng H\u00e0 (2 tuy\u1ebfn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 tuy\u1ebfn 1 chi\u1ec1u song song nhau m\u1ed7i tuy\u1ebfn c\u00f3 l\u1ed9 gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 20m).<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u1ea1n V\u00e0nh \u0111ai trong \u2013 3A: T\u1eeb Ng\u00e3 t\u01b0 B\u1ea3y Hi\u1ec1n cho \u0111\u1ebfn H\u01b0\u01a1ng L\u1ed9 2 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i l\u00e0 4,7 km. Bao g\u1ed3m tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng: \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a Ng\u00e3 t\u01b0 B\u1ea3y Hi\u1ec1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u00c2u C\u01a1, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng H\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ed9 2.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8146 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/pvd.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u00f4ng tin quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t 2021\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8146\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/pvd.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u00f4ng tin quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t 2021\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u1ea1n V\u00e0nh \u0111ai trong \u2013 3B: B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng H\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ed9 2 t\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Linh tr\u1ea3i d\u00e0i l\u00e0 8,4 km (v\u1edbi l\u1ed9 gi\u1edbi 60m). G\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sau: tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa H\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ed9 2 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1 29; \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa Kinh D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0\u00a0 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Linh; \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0111ai trong.\u00a0<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0110ai 1<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u2013 \u00a0 \u00a0 Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch ph\u00e2n t\u00e1n d\u00e2n c\u01b0 t\u1edbi khu v\u1ef1c ven trung t\u00e2m TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u2013 \u00a0 \u00a0 L\u00e0m t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m B\u0110S \u1edf c\u00e1c khu v\u1ee5c xung quanh \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u2013 \u00a0 \u00a0 Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh s\u00e1t TP.HCM c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u2013 \u00a0 \u00a0 Gi\u00fap kinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh khu v\u1ef1c ven TP ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u2013 \u00a0 \u00a0 Gi\u00fap khu v\u1ef1c n\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ea3i xe l\u01b0u th\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8148 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/tin-moi-nhat-ve-duong-vanh-dai-1.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u00f4ng tin quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t 2021\" width=\"800\" height=\"449\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/449;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8148\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/tin-moi-nhat-ve-duong-vanh-dai-1.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u00f4ng tin quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t 2021\" width=\"800\" height=\"449\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u2013 \u00a0 \u00a0 Gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea3i l\u01b0u th\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh ven TP kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng trong n\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u2013 \u00a0 \u00a0 Gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng khu v\u1ef1c ngo\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1eddi k\u1ebft! Th\u00f4ng qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/vinhomeland.com.vn\"><strong>vinhomeland.com.vn<\/strong><\/a>, qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1<strong> \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng V\u00e0nh \u0110ai 1<\/strong>\u00a0c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn B\u0110S khu v\u1ef1c xung quanh. \u0110\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 hay kh\u00f4ng. Hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y mang \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ed5 \u00edch cho b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c B\u0110S nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-right kksr-valign-bottom\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;right&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;8120&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;greet&quot;:&quot;\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft&quot;,&quot;legend&quot;:&quot;5\\\/5 - (1 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;20&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Th\u00f4ng tin quy ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0nh \u0111ai 1 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t 2021&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:&quot;118&quot;,&quot;_legend&quot;:&quot;{score}\\\/{best} - ({count} {votes})&quot;,&quot;font_factor&quot;:&quot;1.25&quot;}'>\n            \n<div class=\"kksr-stars\">\n    \n<div class=\"kksr-stars-inactive\">\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"1\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <div class=\"kksr-star\" data-star=\"2\" style=\"padding-right: 4px\">\n            \n\n<div class=\"kksr-icon\" style=\"width: 20px; height: 20px;\"><\/div>\n        <\/div>\n           